.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-SET-ALL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-set-all \- set fees on all channels at once
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-set-all
.I base_msat ppm
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets the base fee and proportional fee on every channel via
.BR "setchannel all" .
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-fee (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-policy (1)
